ir, and I could not look after it myself. It seems to me that, if you wish\u00A0to go to law about it, you should proceed by the\u00A0usual methods, as is reasonable, taking care to protect yourself by every means in your power. For the expenses to be incurred, I will not fail you as long as I have money to spend. Be as little fearful as you can, for these are not cases in which life itself is endangered. Nothing more. As I have already said, let me hear your views.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"66343a34-8cf3-4590-9ece-5a9d6185f6cb","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":15,"end":23,"value":"0506a75d-a6a0-499f-9721-8261ae330277","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"6c5a90a0-98e7-498d-a56a-da3b3776f6f5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":36,"end":36,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9b400ee5-e589-454a-978e-d5f9f0eb1947","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":90,"end":90,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"287c4776-9ab3-4447-b428-62edb2d6119e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":150,"end":157,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"bda30cf1-462c-4d5d-a62c-cf411c71d142","type":"style/italics","start":219,"end":224,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"5178f61c-0f75-4838-8b2a-18cf6e5fe57b","type":"language","start":219,"end":224,"value":"it","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a45aab21-3c58-4d9f-930e-2740870bb3bf","type":"style/italics","start":257,"end":263,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3e4fa8ad-f567-430c-a1ba-46024262b6eb","type":"language","start":257,"end":263,"value":"it","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"bcfbdaa1-f6e4-437d-8329-229b007b7307","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":293,"end":293,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"efe661f2-4077-43de-a11f-7861f0021a38","type":"codex/entity-reference","start